f Linear Representations in Large Language Models](2403.03867_Origins_of_Linear_Representations.pdf)\n   - Authors: Yibo Jiang et al.\n   - Year: 2024\n   - arXiv: 2403.03867\n   - Why relevant: Theoretical grounding for why independent concepts are represented orthogonally.\n\n8. [The Information Geometry of Softmax: Probing and Steering](2602.15293_Information_Geometry_Softmax.pdf)\n   - Authors: Kiho Park et al.\n   - Year: 2026\n   - arXiv: 2602.15293\n   - Why relevant: Latest work on information geometry and steering LLMs.\n"}}
